! Block all Punycode (xn--) domains — these are NOT normal websites and are commonly used for homograph/phishing attacks
/xn--/$all,important

! Non-ASCII characters in FQDN — not a standard ASCII domain
! High risk of IDN homograph / phishing attacks
/^[a-z]+:\/\/[^\/]*[^\x00-\x7F][^\/]*/$document,important
